                                         Dosen Pembimbing

                                         (................................................)
                                         NIP/NIK: ............................`
  },
  aktif: {
    title: "Surat Keterangan Mahasiswa Aktif",
    file: "/templates/template-surat-keterangan-aktif.docx",
    iconBg: "linear-gradient(135deg,#e0f2fe,#bae6fd)",
    iconColor: "#0369a1",
    iconPath: `<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0369a1" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/></svg>`,
    content: `INSTITUT SHANTI BHUANA
